=Check whether this candidate video duplicates any past video.

=== PAST VIDEOS (recent first) ===
{{ JSON.stringify($json.dedup_context || []) }}

=== CANDIDATE ===
Title: {{ $json.idea_title }}
Summary: {{ $json.idea_one_line_summary }}
Hook: {{ $json.idea_hook }}

Rules: 'Substantially the same' = same core insight even if framing differs. Different example same insight = duplicate. Same topic different insight = NOT duplicate. Moderately strict, not paranoid.

Return ONLY valid JSON: { "duplicate": true|false, "similar_to": "title or null", "reason": "one sentence" }

